    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this absolute gem. This car is in pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve truly babied it since day one, and it still looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, and the interior is completely spotless. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been deeply loved and meticulously maintained, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
